    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>tomatoes</strong> finely and add them to the onion with the <strong>baharat</strong> and a half <span class=\"text-danger\">[whole]</span> <strong>stock cube</strong> and cook for a further 4 min</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the&nbsp;stalks and add the chopped stalks to the pan (save the chopped leaves for later)</p>",
